name: Establish Secret Base (V)
Lore: 'The Empire''s remote bases develop new technology and hide sensitive projects from potential Rebel saboteurs.',
Text: 'If you control Bunker, deploy on Endor system. At each Endor site you control with an AT-ST or Biker Scout, opponent''s Force generation is canceled. During your deploy phase, may deploy one Aratech Corporation or an Effect with ''Endor'' in the lore or game text from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)',
